718
00:43:15,708 --> 00:43:17,251
Oh... masasabi mo ba ito?

719
00:43:18,387 --> 00:43:20,306
"Ang kulit ni Ella."

720
00:43:20,720 --> 00:43:21,970
Si Ella ay isang asong babae.

721
00:43:21,995 --> 00:43:23,496
Oh! Nakumpirma!

722
00:43:23,731 --> 00:43:25,358
Si Freya ang nagsabi, hindi ikaw.

723
00:43:26,128 --> 00:43:26,962
Bakit mo siya kasama?

724
00:43:27,115 --> 00:43:28,115
Mica?

725
00:43:28,522 --> 00:43:29,522
Uh-uh-uh!

726
00:43:29,860 --> 00:43:30,860
Manatili ka dyan!

727
00:43:30,969 --> 00:43:32,428
Dapat 10 talampakan ang layo mo kay Mica.

728
00:43:32,808 --> 00:43:34,685
Tumalikod! Tumalikod!

729
00:43:34,866 --> 00:43:36,363
Ilipat pa! doon!

730
00:43:36,739 --> 00:43:38,032
Hindi siya maaaring manatili dito.

731
00:43:38,954 --> 00:43:40,200
Nasisiraan ka na ba ng bait?

732
00:43:40,617 --> 00:43:42,786
Hindi ako papayag sa Section D
may lakad kayo ni Mica!

733
00:43:42,811 --> 00:43:44,647
Hindi tayo pwedeng makialam sa gulo nila.

734
00:43:45,078 --> 00:43:46,078
Jay-jay?

735
00:43:47,213 --> 00:43:49,131
Gusto ko lang humingi ng favor sayo.

736
00:43:50,169 --> 00:43:52,629
Huwag mo nang hayaang mapalapit pa si Calix kay Mica.

737
00:43:52,838 --> 00:43:53,838
Bakit?

738
00:43:54,340 --> 00:43:55,174
Grabe ako...

739
00:43:55,175 --> 00:43:56,675
Napaka-jerk ko!

740
00:43:56,833 --> 00:43:57,593
Hoy!

741
00:43:57,736 --> 00:43:58,779
anong mali?

742
00:43:58,804 --> 00:44:01,265
May 500-meter run tayo ngayon, okay?

743
00:44:01,575 --> 00:44:02,701
saluhin mo ako!

744
00:44:03,136 --> 00:44:04,818
Ano ang mali sa iyo?

745
00:44:05,678 --> 00:44:07,978
Paikutin siya hanggang
naging violet ang mukha niya!

